{"tid":1347043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【你班死蠢，咪被班黑社會單野轉移視線】【小心立法會突然裝修完成】","createTime":"2019-07-22T05:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T05:42:07.000Z","uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6913133a96f70c92e0b15c925448bac73956d357","tid":1347043,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"支共出錢請牛屎佬黑社會打人，係例牌菜「挑動民眾鬥民眾」。<br />\n<br />\n1）<br />\n成個連登嬲爆，而家個個話湧入元朗。<br />\n咁「撤回送中」呢？突然無人注意到？<br />\n你地班連登仔已經被支共成功轉移視線，<br />\n只focus喺「何妖」同「元朗」<br />\n什麼5大訴求，已經突然遺忘了。<br />\n支共成功左鳥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）<br />\n仲有，個個湧入元朗，即係港島又平靜落嚟。<br />\n什麼金鐘中環灣仔西環突然平靜，有休養生息嘅機會。<br />\n而家政總、狗總、支聯辦、立法會，已經通通安全，水靜鵝飛。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你班死蠢，立法會而家裝修緊。<br />\n10月1日前如果突然裝修完，<br />\n如果突然用得返，<br />\n如果突然二讀，<br />\n送中都有機會通過，話唔定。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咪撚中支共詭計啦屌你老母連登仔"},{"pid":"8cc9cb424468799df29b52bf07c59f2034d64155","tid":1347043,"uid":176112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:20:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4445dd6de07eb533a45920d1f73d48fd269604c0","tid":1347043,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"［無政府狀態］元朗恐怖襲擊將成民間自治催産士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1346084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1346084</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"47f58be5636822e7274a9d250f4560ed93cfdf74","tid":13